C++11 字符串初始化
  C++11 允许将列表初始化用于 C-风格字符串和 string 对象:
    char first_date[] = {"Le Chapon Dodu"};
    char second_date[] {"The Elegant Plate"};
    string third_date[] = {"The Bread Bowl"};
    string fourth_date[] = {"Hank's Fine Eats"};

